FBIS3-32952 "drlat032_o_94012" FBIS-LAT-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 Colombia Foreign Minister: Ties With Venezuela `Very Best' PA1502213494 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in Spanish 1200 GMT 15 Feb 94 PA1502213494 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From "Caracol's 0600 to 0900" newscast] [Text] Foreign Minister Noemi Sanin has said relations with Venezuela are the very best. Sanin has made these statements in response to those made by former Venezuelan Foreign Minister Fernando Ochoa Antich, who has said: Colombia causes us problems.
